'''艾倫·鮑'''（{{lang-en|'''Ellen Pao'''}}，{{bd|1970年|}}），[[漢名|漢名]]'''鮑康如'''<ref name=Streitfeld>Streitfeld, David. "硅谷性別歧視案女高管鮑康如敗訴." [[纽约时报|纽约时报]]中文版. 2015年03月29日. [http://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20150329/c29kleiner/zh-hant/ 繁体字] ([http://www.webcitation.org/6ZoZg8Fue Archive])/[http://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20150329/c29kleiner/zh-hans/ 简体字] ([http://www.webcitation.org/6ZoZxRDpc Archive]). 英文版："[http://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20150329/c29kleiner/en-us/ Ellen Pao Loses Silicon Valley Bias Case Against Kleiner Perkins]" ([http://www.webcitation.org/6ZoZzrZlV Archive]).</ref>，[[美籍华人|美籍华裔]]律师、企业高管，曾任[[Reddit|Reddit]]的臨時[[CEO|CEO]]<ref name=Ohaniancominghome>{{cite web|url = http://www.redditblog.com/2014/11/coming-home.html|title = Reddit Blog: Coming home|date = 2014-11-13|accessdate = 2014-11-13|website = blog.reddit -- what's new on reddit|publisher = |last = Ohanian|first = Alexis|authorlink = 亞歷克西斯·瓦尼安|archive-date = 2014-11-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141113230606/http://www.redditblog.com/2014/11/coming-home.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。她曾任[[Flipboard|Flipboard]]公司董事和[[凱鵬華盈|凱鵬華盈]]的[[合伙人|合伙人]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/ellenhuet/2015/02/25/kleiner-perkins-trial-ski-trip-dinner-party/ |title=Kleiner Perkins Trial Details Firm's All-Male Ski Trip And Dinner Party |publisher=Forbes |date=2015-02-25 |accessdate=2015-03-06 |archive-date=2021-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429124827/https://www.forbes.com/sites/ellenhuet/2015/02/25/kleiner-perkins-trial-ski-trip-dinner-party/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Ohaniancominghome/><ref name="paoNYT">{{cite news | url=http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/04/11/ellen-pao-who-sued-kleiner-perkins-joins-reddit/ | newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | first=David | last=Streitfeld | title=Ellen Pao, Who Sued Kleiner Perkins, Joins Reddit | date=2013-04-11 | accessdate=2015-07-06 | archive-date=2014-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140304053721/http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/04/11/ellen-pao-who-sued-kleiner-perkins-joins-reddit/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Elias, Paul. [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/19/ellen-pao-lawsuit_n_1688208.html Ellen Pao Lawsuit: Sexual Harassment Case Roils Silicon Valley] {{Wayback|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/19/ellen-pao-lawsuit_n_1688208.html |date=20160308202932 }} July 19, 2012 Huffington Post (Associated Press)</ref>

==生平==
1970年出生在美国[[新泽西|新泽西]]，在鲍家三姐妹中排行老二。祖籍河北[[保定|保定]]。父亲鲍永平是[[纽约大学|纽约大学]][[科朗数学研究所|科朗数学研究所]]教授，母亲是[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]]的计算机工程师。1987年鲍康如高三时父亲去世。外祖父早年毕业于[[中华民国陆军军官学校|中华民国陆军军官学校]]，随后成为[[国民党|国民党]]的指挥官，1948年随国民党迁到台湾，1960年退休，官衔[[陆军|陆军]][[上校|上校]]，1972年10月来到美国[[纽约|纽约]]，与早已来美国的鮑康如的母亲团聚。

2013年，鮑康如加入Reddit。2014年11月，在[[黃易山|黃易山]]辭職後，擔任Reddit臨時執行長。2015年7月10日，鮑康如辞任Reddit临时CEO。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title = An old team at reddit • /r/announcements|url = https://www.reddit.com/r/announcements/comments/3cucye/an_old_team_at_reddit/|website = reddit|accessdate = 2015-07-10|archive-date = 2015-07-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150710212352/https://www.reddit.com/r/announcements/comments/3cucye/an_old_team_at_reddit/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>Newcomer, Eric. "[http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2015-07-10/ellen-pao-resigns-as-reddit-interim-ceo-after-user-revolt Ellen Pao Resigns as Reddit Interim CEO After User Revolt]" ([http://www.webcitation.org/6ZxbOOyrv Archive]). ''[[Bloomberg_Business|Bloomberg Business]]''. 2015-07-10.</ref>

2015年，{{link-en|鮑康如控告凱鵬華盈|Pao v. Kleiner Perkins}}性别歧视，法院判決敗訴。<ref name=Streitfeld/>9月10日，鮑康如宣布放棄[[上訴|上訴]]。<ref>[http://style.sina.com.cn/news/b/2012-11-28/0946110361.shtml] {{Wayback|url=http://style.sina.com.cn/news/b/2012-11-28/0946110361.shtml |date=20180209063649 }}，简介。</ref>

